#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.round_.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.round\\_"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around:1 of
msgid "Evenly round to the given number of decimals."
msgstr "将数值均匀舍入到指定的小数位数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around:3 of
msgid "Input data."
msgstr "输入数据。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around:5 of
msgid ""
"Number of decimal places to round to (default: 0).  If decimals is "
"negative, it specifies the number of positions to the left of the decimal"
" point."
msgstr ""
"要舍入的小数位数（默认值：0）。如果 decimals 为负数，则表示小数点左侧的"
"位数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around:9 of
msgid ""
"Alternative output tensor in which to place the result. It must have the "
"same shape as the expected output, but the type of the output values will"
" be cast if necessary."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的替代输出 tensor。它必须与预期输出具有相同的形状，但必要时会"
"转换输出值的类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around:14 of
msgid ""
"**rounded_array** -- An tensor of the same type as `a`, containing the "
"rounded values. Unless `out` was specified, a new tensor is created.  A "
"reference to the result is returned.  The real and imaginary parts of "
"complex numbers are rounded separately.  The result of rounding a float "
"is a float."
msgstr ""
"**rounded_array** -- 一个与 `a` 类型相同的 tensor，包含舍入后的值。除非"
"指定了 `out`，否则将创建一个新的 tensor。返回结果的引用。复数的实部和虚"
"部分别进行舍入。浮点数舍入的结果仍为浮点数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around:14 of
msgid ""
"**rounded_array** -- An tensor of the same type as `a`, containing the "
"rounded values. Unless `out` was specified, a new tensor is created.  A "
"reference to the result is returned."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around:18 of
msgid ""
"The real and imaginary parts of complex numbers are rounded separately.  "
"The result of rounding a float is a float."
msgstr "复数的实部和虚部分别进行舍入。浮点数舍入的结果是浮点数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Tensor.round`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around:25 of
msgid "equivalent method"
msgstr "等效方法"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around:27 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`ceil`, :py:obj:`fix`, :py:obj:`floor`, :py:obj:`rint`, "
":py:obj:`trunc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around:30 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.around.around:31 of
msgid ""
"For values exactly halfway between rounded decimal values, NumPy rounds "
"to the nearest even value. Thus 1.5 and 2.5 round to 2.0, -0.5 and 0.5 "
"round to 0.0, etc. Results may also be surprising due to the inexact "
"representation of decimal fractions in the IEEE floating point standard "
"[1]_ and errors introduced when scaling by powers of ten."
msgstr ""
"对于恰好位于两个舍入小数值中间的值，NumPy 会舍入到最近的偶数。因此，1.5 "
"和 2.5 舍入为 2.0，-0.5 和 0.5 舍入为 0.0，等等。由于 IEEE 浮点标准 [1]_ "
"中十进制分数的非精确表示以及按十的幂次缩放时引入的误差，结果可能令人意外"
"。"

